CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, St. Louis edition, August 16, 1947, pg. 17, reads: "Still More Night of Stars - ...Beside her is sultry Savannah Churchill, famed singing star... - Teenie Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Savannah Churchill wearing light colored gown, singing on stage at Syria Mosque for "Night of Stars" program
